title: Active@ Data Studio 7.5.3 with serial
description:
<a href="http://i.imgur.com/IXERSfi.png" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://i.imgur.com/IXERSfi.png</a>

Here's the latest update of Active@ Data Studio. It contains a set of both desktop applications and a bootable image for booting up any system into a DOS or Windows environment.

Whether you need to perform data recovery, data imaging, or to securely erase data, Active@ Data Studio allows you to run the utilities from within Windows or to boot a system up from a self-contained boot environment.

Key Features:
- new! Boot Disk Creator improved:
- new! The latest software versions: Active@ Disk Image 5.5.2; Active@ KillDisk 7.5.0; Active@ File Recovery 11.0.5; Active@ Partition Recovery 9.0.4; Active@ Partition Manager 2.6.5; Active@ Data Burner 4.0.5; Active@ Disk Editor 3.0.9.
- new! Optimized package size, more compact installation
- Boot Disk Creator creates password protected boot disks and can pre-configure Network Settings (Static IP, etc..)
- Dual-boot functionality (DOS + Windows)
